      "form_guide": "",
      "comment": "I'M FREE (1) is a sprinter who excels over the short dashes. Finished third latest over 498m at this track (29.06) in a OPEN but is better suited here over less ground. Solid record here at this trip including seven wins. Speedy beginner who should be in the action early off the inside. Expected to feature in the finish again. VILLAIN OF FIRE (2) is a well performed dog and winner of seven races who was in the minor money last time out at this track (22.02). Form here at the trip sound including seven wins. Has never been out of the placings from two starts out of this box. Expecting another good run. FARMOR BACARDI (7) has been in top form at this track with back to back wins, scoring in a lightning 21.53 followed by a 21.85 win last time. Flying and looks a key chance again. GOLDEN ENVY (8) finished in the placings last start and deserves some thought.",
